title: Tanya Branning returning to EastEnders? Lauren drops major hint
text:
COMEBACK? Tanya Branning could return to EastEnders 
The EastEnders star left in 2013 and has made several cameos since her official departure. 
But last night, fans were led to believe that she could be back. 
Tanya's daughter Lauren Branning spoke about her son Louie, saying that her mum was missing out on seeing him grow up. 
She explained that Tanya only saw her grandson through video chats and hadn't actually met him properly. 
bbc FAMILY: Lauren said Tanya was missing out on not seeing Louie Sexiest soap stars Wednesday, 22nd June 2016 Check out our gallery on the sexiest soap stars of our time, from Brooke Vincent to Jennifer Metcalfe 1 / 11 Brooke Vincent, best known for playing Sophie Webster in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street “Any chance Tanya comes back on EastEnders?” EastEnders viewer 
The long conversation about the missing character made many fans believe that she's due for a comeback. 
"Too much mention of Tanya. Kinda hinting she'll be popping up in the coming weeks," one tweeted. 
Another posted: "Any chance Tanya comes back on EastEnders?" 
"Is that some sort of hint Tanya will be coming back?" a third agreed.
